  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.6.9">
<l>ūṉiṭaic cuvarvait teṉputūṇ nāṭṭi</l>
<l>yurōmamvēyn toṉpatu vācal</l>
<l>tāṉuṭaik kurampaip piriyumpō tuṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>caraṇamē caraṇameṉ ṟiruntēṉ</l>
<l>tēṉuṭaik kamalat tiruviṉuk karacē</l>
<l>tiraikoḷmā neṭuṅkaṭal kiṭantāy</l>
<l>nāṉuṭait tavattāl tiruvaṭi yaṭaintēṉ</l>
<l>naimicā raṇiyat tuḷentāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having placed flesh inside as walls, fixed bone pillars,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] thatched [with] hair,</l>
<l>At the time this hovel with nine gateways disintegrates,</l>
<l rend="indent">I had thought, “Only refuge with you is refuge.”</l>
<l>Ruler of Tiru of the nectar-laden lotus, you who sleeps</l>
<l rend="indent">in the vast sea with waves,</l>
<l>Through the penitential (strength) that I have, I took refuge</l>
<l rend="indent">at your divine feet, my father in Naimiśāraṇyam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
